Class BaseViewModel

  • java.lang.Object
    • androidx.lifecycle.ViewModel
      • androidx.lifecycle.AndroidViewModel
        • dev.aidaco.parked.Utils.BaseViewModel
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    AddNewUserViewModel, AddNewVehicleViewModel, BuildViewModel, DisplayTicketViewModel, LoginViewModel, ManagerHomeViewModel, ParkVehicleViewModel, SpotDetailViewModel, TicketDetailViewModel, UserDetailViewModel, UserHomeViewModel 

    public abstract class BaseViewModel
extends androidx.lifecycle.AndroidViewModel
    Defines base logic and utilities needed by viewmodels.

    It is recommended that ViewModels inherit from this class.

    Author:
    Aidan Courtney
